I know that my child's physical and mental wellness depends on his food habits. And to improve his immunity system, it’s really important to include healthy food in his daily routine. But as we all know that in today's world where junk food is more tempting compared to healthy food. So, it becomes very difficult to make them have healthy food.

So, I have visited KD Blossom to learn how to make healthy food likeable to my child. And I am so grateful to Dr. Snehal Patel for giving me the right guidance.
